      "name": "Pistachio Paste",
      "amount": "1 tablespoon"
    },
    {
      "name": "Garlic Powder",
      "amount": "1/2 teaspoon"
    },
    {
      "name": "Almond Butter",
      "amount": "1/4 cup"
    },
    {
      "name": "Avocado Oil",
      "amount": "2 tablespoons"
    },
    {
      "name": "Sugar-Free Dijon Mustard",
      "amount": "1 tablespoon"
    },
    {
      "name": "Coconut Flour",
      "amount": "1/4 cup"
    },
    {
      "name": "Almond Milk",
      "amount": "3 tablespoons"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Preheat your oven to 350°F (175°C).",
    "In a mixing bowl, combine the Pistachio Paste, Garlic Powder, Almond Butter, and Sugar-Free Dijon Mustard.",
    "Gradually add in Coconut Flour and Almond Milk, stirring until fully combined without lumps.",
    "Once well blended, transfer the mixture to an oven-safe dish. Let it rest for 10 minutes to set slightly.",
    "Broil the mixture under preheated heat for about 5-7 minutes or until golden brown around the edges.",
    "Serve hot with crusty bread or as a dip for raw veggies."
